Class AlgListBox

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Container
        • javax.swing.JComponent
          • javax.swing.JList<Alg>
            • net.hudup.core.alg.ui.AlgListBox
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.Scrollable, AlgListUI

    public class AlgListBox
extends javax.swing.JList<Alg>
implements AlgListUI
    This graphic user interface (GUI) component as a JList shows a list of algorithms. It also allows users to choose and configure algorithms.
    Version:
    10.0
    Author:
    Loc Nguyen
